---
// No props
---

<style>
  .cta-section {
    background: var(--surface-1);
    padding: 6rem 5%;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .cta-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -30%; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 600px; height: 300px;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(127,119,221,0.12) 0%, transparent 65%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .cta-inner {
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .cta-badge {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    background: rgba(45,212,191,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(45,212,191,0.2);
    padding: 5px 14px; border-radius: var(--r-full);
  }
  .cta-badge-dot {
    width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: #2DD4BF;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(45,212,191,0.15);
  }
  .cta-badge-text { font-size: 12px; color: rgba(45,212,191,0.8); font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; }
  .cta-headline {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.03em; color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.12; margin: 0;
  }
  .cta-headline .hl { color: var(--accent); }
  .cta-sub {
    font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 44ch; margin: 0;
  }
  .cta-btns { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }
  .cta-note { font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--text-dim); margin: 0; }
</style>

<section class="cta-section" aria-labelledby="cta-heading">
  <div class="cta-inner">
    <div class="cta-badge">
      <span class="cta-badge-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="cta-badge-text">Kostenloses Erstgespräch</span>
    </div>

    <h2 class="cta-headline" id="cta-heading">
      Bereit für deinen<br/><span class="hl">digitalen Auftritt?</span>
    </h2>

    <p class="cta-sub">
      In einem kurzen Gespräch finden wir heraus, was du brauchst —
      unverbindlich und ohne Agentur-Preis-Schock.
    </p>

    <div class="cta-btns">
      <a href="/kontakt" class="btn-primary">Jetzt Kontakt aufnehmen</a>
      <a href="/leistungen" class="btn-outline">Leistungen ansehen</a>
    </div>

    <p class="cta-note">Antwort innerhalb von 48 Stunden · Direkt von Maurice</p>
  </div>
</section>
